<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Submission Received | Quintrin</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Intake submission received." />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles.css">

  <script>
    document.addEventListener("DOMContentLoaded", () => {
      const params = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search);
      const name = params.get("name");

      if (name) {
        const slot = document.getElementById("name-slot");
        slot.textContent = `Thank you, ${name}.`;
      }
    });
  </script>
</head>

<body>

  <header>
    <div class="nav">
      <div class="logo">QUINTRIN</div>
      <nav>
        <a href="/services">Services</a>
        <a href="/intake">Intake</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main class="container">

    <section>
      <h1>Submission Received</h1>

      <p id="name-slot"><strong>Thank you.</strong></p>

      <p>
  Your submission has been received and an internal review has been initiated
  to assess completeness and scope.
</p>
      </p>

      <p>
        If additional clarification is required, you will be contacted.
        If the submission is suitable for structured review, next steps
        will be outlined directly.
      </p>

      <p>
        No action is required at this time.
      </p>
    </section>

  </main>

  <footer>
    <p>
      Quintrin provides independent data structuring services only.
      No insurance placement, underwriting, or claims services are offered.
    </p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>